dialogueText.dialogue:
No, no, Fighting is not the Vice of these Times;
and as for a little Swaggering -- damn it, I can do it as
well as the best of 'em.

Pray forbear, Sir; here's Company coming that
will satisfie you in every Thing -- Hallo, hallo --

Here, here, here;

As my Satisfaction is compleat, I have none to ask
of Mr. Daffodil . I forgive his Behaviour to me, as it
has hasten'd and confirm'd my Happiness here;
